{"type":"message","id":"2db6b351","parentId":"2e3c3f03","timestamp":"2026-03-28T06:44:03.455Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"只有1个session，而且是当前这个cron任务本身（\"agent:main:cron:3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978\"），没有真正的用户对话。\n\n所以应该执行自主学习任务。让我先搜索企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务等道简网络相关行业的最新动态。","thinkingSignature":"a500bc68dc08f49675b4ead5f5c3d200e291b31d75aeaabddfd24ee0bd13fb0a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_o498hw3tzj4d_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":881,"output":120,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44982,"cost":{"input":0.0002643,"output":0.000144,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0017277299999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774680240051}}
{"type":"message","id":"3f07a4fe","parentId":"2db6b351","timestamp":"2026-03-28T06:44:03.461Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_o498hw3tzj4d_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774680243458}}
{"type":"message","id":"a746e850","parentId":"3f07a4fe","timestamp":"2026-03-28T06:44:10.325Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我需要使用 miaoda-studio-cli search-summary 来搜索相关信息。让我搜索几个关键词：\n\n1. 企业数字化转型最新动态\n2. 智能安防行业动态\n3. 网络系统集成趋势\n4. IT运维服务最新发展\n\n让我并行搜索这些关键词。","thinkingSignature":"a11579d9109be32b051afc094e5dd35f8a773d1daed76d2b30148cd5a4ee0d6c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_eushxfz9rckz_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026 最新政策动态\" --output json 2>/dev/null || echo '{\"error\": \"search failed\"}'","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_eushxfz9rckz_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防行业动态 2026 技术趋势\" --output json 2>/dev/null || echo '{\"error\": \"search failed\"}'","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_eushxfz9rckz_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成 IT运维服务 行业发展趋势 2026\" --output json 2>/dev/null || echo '{\"error\": \"search failed\"}'","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1516,"output":262,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45759,"cost":{"input":0.0004548,"output":0.0003144,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00208863}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774680243461}}
